{"id": 2052, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你在什么情况下会不那么在意品牌出身？", "description": "金斧头银斧头，我还是选最趁手的铁斧头。（题图来自：GIPHY）", "record_count": 12716, "comment_count": 35, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201712061645065IaCJukPFTDEgVmX.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-07T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3392, "title": "现如今，你在什么情况下会不那么在意品牌出身？", "content": "现如今，你在什么情况下会不那么在意品牌出身？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 252885, "content": "赶时髦买流行单品，穿一季就拉倒，买快时尚也ok", "image": "img/option/option/20171206164644rhVUTlPqsHpfwGIL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252886, "content": "反正接口/型号一样，充电线/转换器不一定买原装", "image": "img/option/option/20171206164711sTeNMBpKzoILnY59.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252889, "content": "买卫生纸、洗衣液啥的日用品，哪个搞活动下单哪个", "image": "img/option/option/20171206165057MFpz3Nd7vQErxPTs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252890, "content": "贴身穿着不外露的衣物，袜子秋裤居家服", "image": "img/option/option/20171206165215zxcYCFMKaAq3L7oT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252891, "content": "家居用品看重实用性，在谁家买没所谓", "image": "img/option/option/201712061652357JaO63ZDMBNusirC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252892, "content": "网红零食，豆乳盒子半熟芝士哪都在卖，味道差不多", "image": "img/option/option/20171206165300LtcfaxSPEj3h7UKF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252893, "content": "买书，主要参考版本和作者/译者，出版社都好说", "image": "img/option/option/201712061653249Br4Qcf1wvWq58gi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252895, "content": "点外卖，更看重口味和价格，不一定要连锁品牌", "image": "img/option/option/20171206165347THlUfteok3x8i9nc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}